{"id": "art-25152", "label": "Art. 25152", "title": "Art. 25152", "slug": "art-25152", "content": "<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:4.0pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_222497311\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1421\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_222497311\"><![endif]></span><b\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:black'>Art. 251<sup>52</sup></span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1347531437\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1420\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1347531437\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(1)<span class=SpellE>Competen&#355;a</span> de verificare\na <span class=SpellE>legalit&#259;&#355;ii</span> transform&#259;rii\ntransfrontaliere sub aspectul procedurii pe care o urmeaz&#259; societatea\npersoan&#259; juridic&#259; român&#259; care se transform&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>apar&#355;ine</span> registratorului de la oficiul registrului <span\nclass=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span> în a c&#259;rui raz&#259; teritorial&#259;\neste situat sediul social al <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>.\nPrevederile art. 105 din <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i> nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>265/2022</span><span style='color:black'>, cu <span\nclass=SpellE>excep&#355;ia</span> termenelor de <span class=SpellE>solu&#355;ionare</span>\na cererii, se aplic&#259; în mod corespunz&#259;tor. În scopul exercit&#259;rii\n<span class=SpellE>competen&#355;ei</span> de verificare a <span class=SpellE>legalit&#259;&#355;ii</span>\ntransform&#259;rii transfrontaliere, registratorul consult&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>institu&#355;iile</span> publice competente, inclusiv, dac&#259;\neste cazul, pe cele din statul membru de <span class=SpellE>destina&#355;ie</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1691519149\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1419\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1691519149\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(2)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Societatea\ndepune, potrivit prevederilor art. 84 din <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i>\nnr. </b></span><b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'><span style='color:#1B1B1B'>265/2022</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>, la oficiul registrului <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span>\no cerere de eliberare a certificatului prealabil transform&#259;rii\ntransfrontaliere, <span class=SpellE>înso&#355;it&#259;</span> de\nurm&#259;toarele:</span></b></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1127299299\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1418\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1127299299\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)proiectul de transformare transfrontalier&#259;, în forma\naprobat&#259; de adunarea general&#259; a <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1687091578\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1417\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1687091578\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)raportul/rapoartele administratorilor sau, dup&#259; caz,\nal/ale membrilor directoratului, la care se anexeaz&#259;, dac&#259; este\ncazul, <span class=SpellE>observa&#355;iile</span> <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span>\nsau <span class=SpellE>reprezentan&#355;ilor</span> acestora <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> cele ale <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>/sau creditorilor cu privire la proiectul de\ntransformare transfrontalier&#259; <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>, dac&#259;\neste cazul, opinia <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span> sau <span\nclass=SpellE>reprezentan&#355;ilor</span> acestora <span class=SpellE>fa&#355;&#259;</span>\nde raportul prev&#259;zut la art. 251<sup>44</sup> sau, dup&#259; caz, acordul <span\nclass=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span> cu privire la <span class=SpellE>renun&#355;area</span>\nîntocmirii raportului <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>/sau dovezi care s&#259;\nateste îndeplinirea <span class=SpellE>condi&#355;iilor</span> prev&#259;zute\nla art. 251<sup>44</sup> alin. (3);</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_739508551\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1416\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_739508551\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)raportul de evaluare al expertului independent sau,\ndup&#259; caz, acordul <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span> cu privire la\n<span class=SpellE>renun&#355;area</span> întocmirii acestuia;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1997862073\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1415\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1997862073\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)hot&#259;rârea adun&#259;rii generale privind aprobarea\ntransform&#259;rii transfrontaliere a <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_900511308\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1414\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_900511308\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e)dac&#259; este cazul, <span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span>\nprivind îndeplinirea <span class=SpellE>cerin&#355;elor</span> legale\nreferitoare la participarea <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;ilor</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> la alte <span class=SpellE>modalit&#259;&#355;i</span>\nde implicare a acestora, inclusiv, dac&#259; este cazul, privind începerea\nprocedurii de negociere, potrivit prevederilor Hot&#259;rârii Guvernului nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>187/2007</span><span style='color:black'>, precum <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> cu privire la num&#259;rul de <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;i</span>\nla momentul întocmirii proiectului de transformare;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_621296169\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1413\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_621296169\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>f)înscrisuri ce atest&#259; constituirea <span\nclass=SpellE>garan&#355;iilor</span> potrivit proiectului de transformare <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span>/sau ca urmare a notific&#259;rii <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> de c&#259;tre creditori, potrivit\nprevederilor art. 251<sup>50</sup> alin. (1), sau, dac&#259; este cazul,\npotrivit hot&#259;rârii <span class=SpellE>judec&#259;tore&#351;ti</span>,\nprecum <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> hot&#259;rârea\njudec&#259;toreasc&#259;, în copie;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_544396085\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1412\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_544396085\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>g)înscrisuri ce atest&#259; <span class=SpellE>existen&#355;a</span>\ndisponibilului pentru plata, în termenul legal, a <span class=SpellE>pre&#355;ului</span>\n<span class=SpellE>ac&#355;iunilor</span>, <span class=SpellE>p&#259;r&#355;ilor</span>\nsociale sau altor titluri de valoare reprezentând capitalul social ale <span\nclass=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span> care <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>-au\nexercitat dreptul de retragere <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>, dac&#259;\neste cazul, a <span class=SpellE>compensa&#355;iei</span> <span class=SpellE>b&#259;ne&#351;ti</span>\nstabilite prin hot&#259;râre judec&#259;toreasc&#259;, precum <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> hot&#259;rârea judec&#259;toreasc&#259;, în copie;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_901263253\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1411\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_901263253\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>h)dac&#259; a fost introdus&#259; o cerere în anulare sau\nde declarare a <span class=SpellE>nulit&#259;&#355;ii</span> hot&#259;rârii\nadun&#259;rii generale a <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;ilor</span> de aprobare\na transform&#259;rii transfrontaliere, hot&#259;rârea judec&#259;toreasc&#259;\nprin care este respins&#259; cererea, în copie;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_975565592\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1410\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_975565592\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>i)<span class=SpellE>declara&#355;ia</span> pe propria\nr&#259;spundere a administratorilor sau, dup&#259; caz, a membrilor\ndirectoratului prin care confirm&#259; c&#259;, potrivit datelor <span\nclass=SpellE>de&#355;inute</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nverific&#259;rilor efectuate în baza principiului <span class=SpellE>pruden&#355;ei</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>diligen&#355;ei</span>\nbunului administrator, <span class=SpellE>situa&#355;ia</span> financiar&#259;\na <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, la data <span class=SpellE>declara&#355;iei</span>,\npermite realizarea transform&#259;rii transfrontaliere, c&#259; societatea are\ncapacitatea de a executa <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iile</span> scadente <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iile</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>fa&#355;&#259;</span> de <span class=SpellE>asocia&#355;i</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> creditori, potrivit <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span>\nart. 251<sup>49</sup> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> 251<sup>50</sup>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2100647034\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1409\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2100647034\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(3)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Registrul\noficiului <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span> <span class=SpellE>ob&#355;ine</span>\ndin registrele <span class=SpellE>&#355;inute</span> de acesta <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> de la alte <span class=SpellE>institu&#355;ii</span>\npublice, pe cale <span class=SpellE>interinstitu&#355;ional&#259;</span>, în\nscopul verific&#259;rii de c&#259;tre registrator a <span class=SpellE>legalit&#259;&#355;ii</span>\ntransform&#259;rii transfrontaliere, urm&#259;toarele:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1473403617\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1408\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1473403617\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)certificatul de atestare fiscal&#259;, care s&#259;\nateste executarea <span class=SpellE>obliga&#355;iilor</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> ce face obiectul transform&#259;rii\nc&#259;tre bugetul de stat <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> bugetele locale;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1927379042\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1407\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1927379042\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)<span class=SpellE>informa&#355;iile</span> din cazierul\nfiscal;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1847725037\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1406\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1847725037\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>c)<span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span> din cazierul\njudiciar;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_869012593\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1405\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_869012593\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>d)<span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span> din sistemul <span\nclass=SpellE>na&#355;ional</span> integrat de <span class=SpellE>eviden&#355;&#259;</span>\na <span class=SpellE>crean&#355;elor</span> provenite din <span class=SpellE>infrac&#355;iuni</span>\n- ROARMIS;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_3343477\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1404\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_3343477\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>e)<span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span> privind\nnum&#259;rul de filiale <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> amplasarea\ngeografic&#259; a acestora;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1498438897\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1403\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1498438897\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>f)<span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span> privind\nnum&#259;rul de <span class=SpellE>angaja&#355;i</span>;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_274382746\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1402\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_274382746\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>g)<span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span> privind <span\nclass=SpellE>sanc&#355;iunile</span> <span class=SpellE>contraven&#355;ionale</span>\naplicate <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, potrivit <span\nclass=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span> art. 53 <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\n54 din <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i> nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>217/2005</span><span style='color:black'>,\nrepublicat&#259;, cu modific&#259;rile <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\ncomplet&#259;rile ulterioare, <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>/sau potrivit <span\nclass=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span> art. 9 <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\n10 din <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i> nr. </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>467/2006</span><span style='color:black'>, cu\nmodific&#259;rile <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> complet&#259;rile\nulterioare;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_628683742\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1401\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_628683742\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>h)<span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span> din registrul\nbeneficiarilor reali privind beneficiarii reali ai <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_34252473\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1400\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_34252473\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(4)Dac&#259; procedurile de derulare a transform&#259;rii\ntransfrontaliere <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>formalit&#259;&#355;ile</span>\nprivind aceast&#259; <span class=SpellE>opera&#355;iune</span> nu sunt\nfinalizate ori dac&#259; nu sunt depuse toate înscrisurile prev&#259;zute de <i\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>lege</i>, registratorul, prin încheiere, în\ntermen de 10 zile de la depunerea cererii, acord&#259; <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nun termen pentru regularizare, care nu poate <span class=SpellE>dep&#259;&#351;i</span>\n15 zile.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1701970172\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1399\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1701970172\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(5)Dac&#259; procedurile de derulare a transform&#259;rii\ntransfrontaliere în statul membru de plecare <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>formalit&#259;&#355;ile</span> privind aceast&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>opera&#355;iune</span> sunt îndeplinite potrivit <i\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legii</i>, iar rapoartele prev&#259;zute la\nart. 251<sup>44</sup> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> 251<sup>45</sup> sunt\nîntocmite potrivit <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>legii</i>,\nregistratorul emite certificatul prealabil transform&#259;rii transfrontaliere,\nal c&#259;rui format se aprob&#259; prin ordin al ministrului <span\nclass=SpellE>justi&#355;iei</span>.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_387594923\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1398\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_387594923\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(6)<b style='mso-bidi-font-weight:normal'>Registratorul\nrespinge, motivat, cererea de emitere a certificatului prealabil\ntransform&#259;rii transfrontaliere:</b></span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1415038895\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1397\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1415038895\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>a)dac&#259; nu au fost îndeplinite <span class=SpellE>cerin&#355;ele</span>\nlegale privind transformarea transfrontalier&#259;, inclusiv în ceea ce <span\nclass=SpellE>prive&#351;te</span> întocmirea, potrivit <i style='mso-bidi-font-style:\nnormal'>legii</i>, a rapoartelor prev&#259;zute la art. 251<sup>44</sup> <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> 251<sup>45</sup>, <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>/sau\nnu au fost depuse înscrisurile ce atest&#259; îndeplinirea acestor <span\nclass=SpellE>cerin&#355;e</span> legale în termenul acordat de registrator;</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-bottom:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_548773830\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1396\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_548773830\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>b)în cazul în care societatea ce face obiectul\ntransform&#259;rii a fost condamnat&#259; definitiv pentru <span class=SpellE>s&#259;vâr&#351;irea</span>\nunei <span class=SpellE>infrac&#355;iuni</span>, iar pedeapsa amenzii sau,\ndup&#259; caz, cea complementar&#259; nu a fost înc&#259; executat&#259;.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_2086610183\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1395\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_2086610183\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(7)Dac&#259; din înscrisurile depuse de societate, din <span\nclass=SpellE>informa&#355;iile</span> <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> din\nînscrisurile aflate în dosarul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>\nde la oficiul registrului <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span> sau din\ncele <span class=SpellE>ob&#355;inute</span> de oficiul registrului <span\nclass=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span> pe cale <span class=SpellE>interinstitu&#355;ional&#259;</span>\nrezult&#259; <span class=SpellE>existen&#355;a</span> unor indicii serioase\nc&#259; <span class=SpellE>opera&#355;iunea</span> transfrontalier&#259; se\nefectueaz&#259; în scopuri abuzive sau frauduloase, ducând sau <span\nclass=SpellE>propunându-&#351;i</span> s&#259; duc&#259; la evaziune sau la\neludarea dreptului Uniunii Europene sau a celui intern ori în scopul <span\nclass=SpellE>s&#259;vâr&#351;irii</span> de <span class=SpellE>infrac&#355;iuni</span>,\nregistratorul sesizeaz&#259; tribunalul în a c&#259;rui <span class=SpellE>circumscrip&#355;ie</span>\nse afl&#259; sediul <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>, pentru a se\n<span class=SpellE>pronun&#355;a</span> asupra cererii de emitere a\ncertificatului prealabil transform&#259;rii transfrontaliere. În acest caz,\ntoate înscrisurile depuse de societate <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> toate\ncele <span class=SpellE>ob&#355;inute</span>, pe cale <span class=SpellE>institu&#355;ional&#259;</span>,\nde oficiul registrului <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span>, precum <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> <span class=SpellE>informa&#355;iile</span>\nrelevante din registrul <span class=SpellE>comer&#355;ului</span> <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> din registrul beneficiarilor reali sunt transmise <span\nclass=SpellE>instan&#355;ei</span> <span class=SpellE>judec&#259;tore&#351;ti</span>\ncompetente.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1294259098\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1394\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1294259098\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(8)Cererea prev&#259;zut&#259; la alin. (7) este <span\nclass=SpellE>solu&#355;ionat&#259;</span> de <span class=SpellE>urgen&#355;&#259;</span>\n<span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> cu prec&#259;dere, în camera de consiliu, cu\ncitarea <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span>. Pentru termenul fixat\nva fi citat <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> parchetul de pe lâng&#259; <span\nclass=SpellE>instan&#355;a</span> sesizat&#259;, c&#259;ruia i se vor comunica,\nîn copie, înscrisurile din dosar. În acest caz punerea concluziilor de\nc&#259;tre procuror este obligatorie.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_1884494252\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1393\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\"\n style='width:12pt;height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_1884494252\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(9)Prin hot&#259;rârea <span class=SpellE>pronun&#355;at&#259;</span>,\npotrivit <span class=SpellE>dispozi&#355;iilor</span> art. 527-540 din <i\nstyle='mso-bidi-font-style:normal'>Legea</i> nr. </span><span style='color:\n#1B1B1B'>134/2010</span><span style='color:black'> privind </span><span\nstyle='color:#1B1B1B'>Codul de procedur&#259; civil&#259;</span><span\nstyle='color:black'>, republicat&#259;, cu modific&#259;rile <span\nclass=SpellE>&#351;i</span> complet&#259;rile ulterioare, dac&#259;\nconstat&#259; îndeplinirea <span class=SpellE>cerin&#355;elor</span> legale\npentru realizarea transform&#259;rii transfrontaliere, <span class=SpellE>instan&#355;a</span>\nadmite cererea <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span> dispune emiterea de c&#259;tre\nregistrator a certificatului prealabil transform&#259;rii transfrontaliere. În\ncazul în care constat&#259; c&#259; transformarea transfrontalier&#259; se\nefectueaz&#259; în scopuri abuzive sau frauduloase, ducând sau <span\nclass=SpellE>propunându-&#351;i</span> s&#259; duc&#259; la înc&#259;lcarea sau\nla eludarea dreptului Uniunii Europene sau a celui intern ori în scopul <span\nclass=SpellE>s&#259;vâr&#351;irii</span> de <span class=SpellE>infrac&#355;iuni</span>,\n<span class=SpellE>instan&#355;a</span> respinge cererea de emitere a\ncertificatului prealabil fuziunii transfrontaliere. Hot&#259;rârea <span\nclass=SpellE>instan&#355;ei</span> este executorie <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\neste supus&#259; numai apelului, care poate fi exercitat <span class=SpellE>&#351;i</span>\nde Ministerul Public.</span></p>\n<p class=MsoNormal style='margin-top:1.3pt;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:0in;\nmargin-left:0in'><span style='mso-no-proof:yes'><!--[if gte vml 1]><v:shape\n id=\"Imagine_x0020_556335899\" o:spid=\"_x0000_i1392\" type=\"#_x0000_t75\" style='width:12pt;\n height:12pt;visibility:visible;mso-wrap-style:square'>\n <v:imagedata src=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image001.png\"\n  o:title=\"\"/>\n</v:shape><![endif]--><![if !vml]><img width=16 height=16\nsrc=\"legea%20societatilor-republicare.files/image002.gif\" v:shapes=\"Imagine_x0020_556335899\"><![endif]></span><span\nstyle='color:black'>(10)Termenul de evaluare a cererii de emitere a\ncertificatului prealabil transform&#259;rii transfrontaliere nu poate <span\nclass=SpellE>dep&#259;&#351;i</span> 3 luni de la data depunerii cererii, cu <span\nclass=SpellE>excep&#355;ia</span> cazului prev&#259;zut la alin. (7), când\nacesta poate fi prelungit cu cel mult 3 luni. Dac&#259;, din cauza <span\nclass=SpellE>complexit&#259;&#355;ii</span> procedurii transfrontaliere sunt\nnecesare <span class=SpellE>informa&#355;ii</span> sau verific&#259;ri\nsuplimentare, iar evaluarea nu poate fi realizat&#259; în aceste termene,\nregistratorul, din oficiu sau, dup&#259; caz, sesizat de <span class=SpellE>instan&#355;&#259;</span>,\ncomunic&#259; <span class=SpellE>societ&#259;&#355;ii</span> motivele eventualelor\nîntârzieri, înainte de expirarea termenelor.</span></p>"}